Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.64,0:00:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.94,0:00:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司被甩了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.39,0:00:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 绘瑠是这么报告的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.11,0:00:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}过去跟他说说话会不会好点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.80,0:00:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我觉得先放他一段时间比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.79,0:00:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}康孝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.68,0:01:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看来受伤很重
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.27,0:01:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}别胡闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.72,0:01:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我只是想要让司打起精神…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.39,0:01:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司 你真的向艾拉告白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.60,0:01:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.76,0:01:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}忽然把你叫出来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.65,0:01:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你… 那个… 没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.90,0:01:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}另外
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.15,0:01:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司真的向你告白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.53,0:01:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且我听说你拒绝他了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.06,0:01:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.79,0:01:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎怎…怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.12,0:01:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我我我…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.24,0:02:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}被告 告 告白了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.61,0:03:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你完全看起来不像没事的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.68,0:03:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我突然就被告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.40,0:03:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}脑子里跳出了许多想法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.93,0:03:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}完全不知道该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.26,0:03:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}顺势就告诉他不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.74,0:04:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}之后司就一直那个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.63,0:04:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就算我向他搭话似乎也听不见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.89,0:04:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他那样子不管谁去搭话都一样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.42,0:04:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这不是艾拉需要在意的事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.85,0:04:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}该说司最近有些得意忘形吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.65,0:04:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}会变成这样肯定大概就是他的错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.21,0:04:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他一定是不会看气氛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.91,0:04:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}突然就跑出来告白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.89,0:04:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我和司在嘉年华会场上走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.92,0:04:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看吧果然是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.54,0:04:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}连好好保护女生都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.60,0:04:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一点用都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.47,0:04:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是他非常拚命地找我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.47,0:04:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}最后找到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.15,0:04:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘛 这是理所应当的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.04,0:04:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}之后就开始放烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.80,0:04:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们一起牵着手看烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.52,0:04:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在那时候牵手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.39,0:04:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还不错…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.24,0:04:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然后顺着话题就被抱住了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.53,0:05:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那可真是激情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.45,0:05:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然后就被告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.51,0:05:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这一点都不浪漫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.18,0:05:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}肯定要拒绝的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.16,0:05:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也会那么做的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.74,0:05:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你脸好红哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.12,0:05:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.37,0:05:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我伤害了司
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.98,0:05:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉想怎么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.16,0:05:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.31,0:05:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果是满会怎么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.96,0:05:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.85,0:05:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我觉得就算你问她也没什么意义
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.44,0:05:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}满又没有被人告白过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.85,0:05:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}够了 别在那多嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.69,0:05:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在司面前你还能像以前一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.45,0:05:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.77,0:05:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我想两个人都应该先冷静下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.46,0:05:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要试试跟司分开过几天吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.74,0:06:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那样的话你也可以好好考虑一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.82,0:06:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对他到底是怎样的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.01,0:06:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}分开…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.67,0:06:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}具体怎么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.09,0:06:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个…现在正在想
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.45,0:06:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}原来你没有计划啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.20,0:06:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天的目标需要小心一点比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.38,0:06:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}持有者引起过暴力事件
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.46,0:06:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是有前科的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.67,0:06:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.76,0:06:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}话说…你知道司向艾拉告白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.60,0:06:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么！ 真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.94,0:06:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}绘瑠告诉我了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.65,0:06:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么时候的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.27,0:06:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}昨天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.16,0:06:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司求婚时说了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.70,0:06:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 不是求婚 是告白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.38,0:06:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那两个家伙 进展到什么程度了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.78,0:06:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你说进展…是指的什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.48,0:06:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.78,0:06:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大概…知道你想说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.50,0:06:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}结果呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.26,0:06:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉似乎拒绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.96,0:07:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拒绝了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.80,0:07:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也没有想到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.50,0:07:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.05,0:07:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你的表情很可怕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.60,0:07:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}闭嘴
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.66,0:07:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}听懂了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.02,0:07:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要是擅自动房间的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.08,0:07:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我可不会轻易饶过你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.18,0:07:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}塞克
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.99,0:07:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要是司做了任何一点可疑的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.35,0:07:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就把他赶出房间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.51,0:07:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吶吶 司
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.29,0:07:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}满的内衣放在这边的抽屉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.82,0:07:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那边是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.89,0:07:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你告诉他干嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.22,0:07:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂 为什么我和司住一间房
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.59,0:07:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在的司气氛那么沉重
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.32,0:07:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我可不想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.43,0:07:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}暂且忍一忍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.23,0:07:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}男生和女生换一下房间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.21,0:07:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我要和绘瑠一起照顾艾拉才行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.77,0:07:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}安慰司就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.49,0:07:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不用做到那种程度
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.81,0:07:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你打算消沉到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.20,0:07:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}给我爽快点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.34,0:07:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}被甩掉而已有什么大不了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.46,0:08:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.06,0:08:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}反正不理你 你也只会坐在那里什么都不吃发呆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.26,0:08:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在我的房间饿死了 我可受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.87,0:08:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我怎么觉得一晚上不吃不喝也死不了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.40,0:08:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你说了什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.78,0:08:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.25,0:08:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吃吧 趁着还没有凉快点吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.08,0:08:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.50,0:08:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哼 我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.90,0:08:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来 艾拉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.22,0:08:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}趁着还没有凉赶快吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.03,0:08:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我可是努力了一把
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.78,0:08:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快点吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.95,0:08:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}比…比起这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.54,0:08:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为什么你给我穿这件衣服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.63,0:08:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.36,0:08:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉拉竟然会来我的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.45,0:08:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}梦想成真了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.25,0:08:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今晚太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.89,0:09:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}完全冷静不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.27,0:09:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}塞克 太不象话了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.82,0:09:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.92,0:09:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.21,0:09:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不认真工作却一心搞职场恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.70,0:09:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}区区一个新人太嚣张了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.31,0:09:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.65,0:09:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这是现在还把自己当学生的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.89,0:09:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我无话可说…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.10,0:09:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我知道你很受打击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.77,0:09:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你要把工作和私生活分开
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.53,0:09:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在像你这样的废柴 去回收和家人一样的吉芙提尔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.31,0:09:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}别人会怎么想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.40,0:09:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我跟你说过我爸爸变成游荡者的事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.39,0:09:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.59,0:09:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我眼睁睁的失去父亲 变成孤零零一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.38,0:09:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽然香月姐来看过我很多次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.71,0:10:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我觉得过意不去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.48,0:10:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就对她说了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.54,0:10:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}「你不用再来了」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.80,0:10:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.91,0:10:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为吉芙提尔和持有者提供心灵依靠是终端服务的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.63,0:10:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我虽然不能代替你的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.30,0:10:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是至少能陪你说说话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.19,0:10:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在你振作起来之前希望你让我这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.48,0:10:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要不然我没办法面对你的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.66,0:10:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我看到那样的香月姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.08,0:10:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才想加入终端服务
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.06,0:10:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我为自己在这里工作感到骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.10,0:10:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以如果你在这里混日子的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.14,0:10:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我饶不了你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.96,0:10:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.38,0:10:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢谢你关心我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.08,0:10:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哼 我只是作为一个前辈指导你而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.09,0:11:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}告白之后后悔了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.98,0:11:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.95,0:11:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽然被拒绝了 但是对艾拉的感情不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.46,0:11:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你还挺执着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.43,0:11:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我觉得你这点很帅…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.51,0:11:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为…为什么我刚才
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.15,0:11:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.10,0:11:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.48,0:11:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}话说你真的懂我在说什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.19,0:11:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}懂的话就别在那里发呆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.98,0:11:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好好想想今后怎么和艾拉接触
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.42,0:11:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.81,0:11:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\blur2\fs37}真的是爱管闲事…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.13,0:11:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你知道什么了说出来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.77,0:11:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我会听着的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.30,0:11:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉拉 今晚不会让你睡的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.53,0:11:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来开睡衣派对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.55,0:11:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好吧 好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.85,0:11:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个…满呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.17,0:11:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.28,0:11:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等下就会来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.19,0:11:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}比起那个 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为了艾拉拉我准备了这么多的睡衣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.23,0:11:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}从哪个开始穿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.33,0:11:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吶 从哪个开始？
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.78,0:12:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}满
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.10,0:12:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.67,0:12:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}睡相
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.97,0:12:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}被看见了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.17,0:12:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可恶 没想到竟然睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.34,0:12:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不快点准备的话要迟到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.96,0:12:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.75,0:12:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为什么不早点叫我起来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.69,0:12:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}总觉得…有点怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.55,0:12:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你这话什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.18,0:12:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我没有在意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.08,0:12:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这不是我该在意的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.26,0:12:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不不 这是误会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.28,0:12:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对 我们并没有做什么下流的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.45,0:12:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没关系 司和满很般配的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.83,0:12:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}糟糕 要赶快追上去才行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.68,0:13:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}振作一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.09,0:13:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}解开了误会真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.57,0:13:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我太冲动弄错了 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.26,0:13:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 要怪也怪我没用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.67,0:13:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}别不说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.44,0:13:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好不容易有这个机会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.55,0:13:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好好聊一下怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.99,0:13:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还是不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.61,0:13:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个…司
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.73,0:13:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎…怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.28,0:13:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.70,0:13:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.36,0:13:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我那时候拒绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.70,0:13:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是想好好考虑一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.51,0:13:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再给我一些时间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.92,0:14:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}当然没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.26,0:14:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是无论艾拉作何决断
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.18,0:14:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请至少让我继续做你的搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.24,0:14:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.93,0:14:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你有什么在意的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.62,0:14:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.48,0:14:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}老爷子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.91,0:14:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你觉得恋爱是不是气势也很重要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.63,0:14:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是指艾拉的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.87,0:14:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我让那孩子好好考虑一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.80,0:14:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但这样真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.42,0:14:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这种事花费太多时间的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.33,0:14:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}会向着坏的方向考虑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.29,0:14:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不知道…究竟怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.84,0:14:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.05,0:14:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.27,0:15:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那我们一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.54,0:15:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.93,0:15:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.45,0:15:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天是什么茶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.92,0:15:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.34,0:15:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你实际上是怎么看待司的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.89,0:15:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.07,0:15:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为什么司总是在笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.54,0:15:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一开始让我在意的是这件事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.99,0:15:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.09,0:15:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}之前满不是也说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.49,0:16:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司可能是因为悲伤而笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.23,0:16:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.68,0:16:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不想让他有那样的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.27,0:16:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}总想着要帮他些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.84,0:16:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是去游乐园的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.47,0:16:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.34,0:16:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.70,0:16:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}从中途心就怦怦地跳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.20,0:16:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.61,0:16:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}从那以后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.42,0:16:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一想到司的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.12,0:16:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我心里就充满紧张和悸动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.77,0:16:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没办法用语言来形容
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.57,0:16:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}很困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.07,0:16:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是吗是吗 果然是这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.88,0:16:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}已经得到答案了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.32,0:16:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你自己也清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.74,0:16:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}答案…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.97,0:16:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 答案早已经有了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.84,0:16:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然 那就赶快去和司说…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.44,0:17:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\blur2\fs38}我要离开司
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.97,0:17:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.32,0:17:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等下 你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.29,0:17:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为什么会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.78,0:17:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我觉得这样做对彼此都很好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.77,0:17:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等等 不对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.34,0:17:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样的话我就跟你明说了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.69,0:17:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你感觉到的这种悸动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.89,0:17:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是恋爱 是恋爱的心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.87,0:17:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}恋爱？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.91,0:17:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以根本不需要离开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.89,0:17:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果是那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.08,0:17:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我更要远离司了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.10,0:17:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不懂 我不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.72,0:17:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}告诉我为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.23,0:17:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么样才能得出这样的结论
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.02,0:17:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.89,0:17:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为…一个月
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.37,0:17:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为我只剩下大概一个月的寿命了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.78,0:18:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哟 你居然没喝醉真是罕见
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.32,0:18:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}别那么瞪着我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.75,0:18:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要是嫌我碍事的话 我会自动消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.70,0:18:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你是不是煽动司了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.88,0:18:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}煽动什么的 太失礼了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.32,0:18:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他只是自己想清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.41,0:18:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}像个男人一样表达出自己的心意而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.29,0:18:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}结果就是那个德行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.75,0:18:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他们俩好不容易才合拍了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.29,0:18:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那么你是打算干涉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.56,0:18:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽然至今一直在逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.72,0:18:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只有这种时候才会装得像个前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.71,0:18:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我这人对于可爱的后辈的事情可是一清二楚的哟
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.19,0:19:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}满？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.35,0:19:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你在这种地方干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.70,0:19:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.91,0:19:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉寿命的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.85,0:19:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你什么时候知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.19,0:19:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是最近
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.12,0:19:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我明明什么都不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.97,0:19:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}却对你和艾拉尽说些自作聪明的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.35,0:19:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.69,0:19:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.10,0:19:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明明应该在工作上已经适应了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.90,0:19:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你说是最近才知道寿命的事的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.52,0:20:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是在告白之前 还是之后
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.69,0:20:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}之前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.47,0:20:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那么 你是明明知道还去告白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.26,0:20:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你做了这个工作以后 到底都看到了些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.84,0:20:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}分手是注定的 而你为什么还要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.22,0:20:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你到底想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.12,0:20:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我想创造和艾拉在一起的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.82,0:20:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想为艾拉创造回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.13,0:20:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明明被甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.13,0:20:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就算如此 我也想为她做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.85,0:20:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你想要做的是非常痛苦的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.60,0:20:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不可能会有什么好结果的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.06,0:20:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就算如此 你也能毫不退缩地面对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.26,0:20:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我…我在爸爸的那时候逃避了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.01,0:20:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没能面对他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.33,0:20:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因此伤害了很多人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.84,0:20:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你能够负责到底吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.42,0:20:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我已经决定 要一直做艾拉的搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.46,0:20:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}直到最后的一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.42,0:21:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}责任的意义 你明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.02,0:21:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.79,0:21:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你和那时的我完全不一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.67,0:21:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是这样我才说外行完全不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.36,0:21:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你…你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.32,0:21:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我在说你是个无药可救的恋爱新手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.68,0:21:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以 我就稍微支持一下你们的恋爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.90,0:21:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好好谢谢我吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.36,0:21:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.23,0:21:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}香月姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.10,0:21:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.14,0:21:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为什么你会在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.02,0:21:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你来得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.72,0:22:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我有话对你说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.26,0:22:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.75,0:22:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.26,0:22:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我被香月叫了过来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.22,0:22:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}从今天起 你们两个解除搭档关系
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.91,0:22:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.53,0:22:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.66,0:22:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没听清楚吗 解除搭档关系
